      "title": "VL-101 latency investigation",
      "messages": [
        { "id": "msg-1", "role": "user", "content": "We're seeing p99 at 2.8s on ticket routing. Started Tuesday after the embedding pipeline change. Priya and I have been digging — we think it's the vector DB connection pool.", "minutesAgo": 130 },
        { "id": "msg-2", "role": "assistant", "content": "That's consistent with pool exhaustion under concurrent embedding requests. What's the pool size set to? And what's the embedding QPS at peak?", "minutesAgo": 128 },
        { "id": "msg-3", "role": "user", "content": "Pool is 20 connections. Peak QPS is ~340/s during US business hours. Each embedding call holds a connection for ~300ms on cold path.", "minutesAgo": 125 },
        { "id": "msg-4", "role": "assistant", "content": "Math checks out — 20 × (1000/300) = ~66 concurrent connections, but you're hitting 340 QPS. Connection pool is saturated. Options: increase pool size, add connection pooling sidecar, or implement embedding request batching. I'd go with batching first — smallest blast radius.", "minutesAgo": 122 }
      ],
      "updatedAtMinutesAgo": 122
    },
    {
      "id": "thread-3",
      "title": "Widget dark mode design review",
      "messages": [
        { "id": "msg-1", "role": "user", "content": "Ava, can you walk us through the dark mode token structure? I want to make sure we're covering contrast ratios for all interactive states before we finalize.", "minutesAgo": 88 },
        { "id": "msg-2", "role": "assistant", "content": "Sure. I've defined 48 tokens across 6 groups: surface (background, card, modal), text (primary, secondary, muted, inverse), border (default, strong, focused), interactive (primary, secondary, danger, ghost), feedback (success, warning, error, info), and overlay (scrim, backdrop). All interactive tokens are WCAG AA at minimum — primary buttons are AAA.", "minutesAgo": 86 },
        { "id": "msg-3", "role": "user", "content": "Looks solid. One gap — the ghost button text on dark surfaces. 'Ghost secondary' text is #64748b on #0f172a — that fails AA at 3.9:1. Should be #94a3b8 minimum.", "minutesAgo": 83 },
        { "id": "msg-4", "role": "assistant", "content": "Good catch. Updated ghost secondary to #94a3b8 — that gets us to 4.6:1. I'll also add a ghost-tertiary for disabled states at #475569 (5.9:1). Pushing the revised token set to Figma now.", "minutesAgo": 80 }
      ],
